lockkey-locking-unforged = This lock is not yet forged!
lockkey-locking-success = You successfully add a lock to the door.

lockkey-forging-lockunforged = The lock you're trying to copy is not yet forged!
lockkey-forging-keyunforged = The key you're trying to copy is not yet forged!
lockkey-forging-lockforged = This lock is already forged!
lockkey-forging-keyforged = This key is already forged!
lockkey-forging-success = The key and the lock are now forged.
lockkey-forging-key-success = The key is now forged to fit the lock.
lockkey-forging-lock-copy-success = The lock is now forged to copy this lock.
lockkey-forging-key-copy-success = The key is now forged to copy this key.

lockkey-no-key = You need to be holding a key to open this!
lockkey-not-forged = You cannot open doors with an unforged key!
lockkey-reader-fail = This key doesn't fit!
